nodes.text: Celebrating 10 Years of Kamino's Finest is an article written by Mark Newbold that appeared in Star Wars Insider 133 in 2012. The article serves to celebrate a decade of clone troopers in the 501st Legion.

Newbold interviewed 501st founder Albin Johnson (USA, 501st Legion, TK 210), Dave G Hildreth (UK, UK Garrison, SL 8511), Nick Bishop (Tasmania, Thylacine Garrison, TK6273) and Adam Santorski (Poland, Polish Garrison, ID 8098).
